SIMPLE: staple_gun
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: staple gun
<hw>sta"ple gun`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A device used to drive a heavy
staple{8} through multiple objects, so as to fasten them together; it
has a spring mechanism which stores force as a lever is pulled by the
operator's hand, and the force is released all at once to drive the
staple fully into the object to be fastened.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stapler</ent>⟦br⟧
